snippet.title: X Rock gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for X Rock, Dos PC game produced by Soft-World in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/x-rock/8396/
Playing through the first stage of this Tetris clone that will uncover cute girls.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
